Author: StressedCookie
Text: I'm the opposite. I feel like a fat fuck at home bc there's food. I still live my parents so it's kind of "Ah I gotta be lowkey about this" I restrict then be scurrying mouse for food in the middle of the night. When I'm busy like going to school, I can just forget about it. I can make excuses.  I ate at home. I ate at school. Plus, I get to save up my allowace.
